ominas_ring__define.pro


NAME: ominas_ring__define PURPOSE: Class structure for the RING class. CATEGORY: NV/LIB/RNG CALLING SEQUENCE: N/A FIELDS: dkd: DISK class descriptor. Methods: rng_disk, rng_set_disk primary: Primary body descriptor. Methods: rng_primary, rng_set_primary desc: String giving the description of the ring. Valid values are 'EDGE', 'PEAK', 'TROUGH'. Methods: rng_desc, rng_set_desc STATUS: Complete MODIFICATION HISTORY: Written by: Spitale, 1/1998 Adapted by: Spitale, 5/2016
